name: ComorbiditiesIndicatedWithCAP
title: Comorbidities Indicated with CAP
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for comorbidities indicated as relevant to community acquired pneumonia.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element in the QDM category of Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that describe comorbidities indicated as relevant to community acquired pneumonia.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
